summary: This mod adds a small cabin in the Whiterun Hold wild. Mainly made for the people who like hunting.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a small cabin in the Whiterun Hold wild. Mainly made for the people who like hunting.

If there are any problems with the mod, please message me and I'll try to fix it as best I can. I know my computers a little slow, so there is some lagging, but all-in-all, it should be okay.  

I might update in the near future as I learn more things.
author: hellacool
